  THE THEORY DOESN'T DIE — IT CRYSTALLIZES.

  The large-n tournament is not a formless blob.
  It's a CRYSTAL with a single vibrational mode (level 2).
  All the complexity of 5-cycles, 7-cycles, etc. fades away,
